casebody.data:
Filed April 21, 1891. Mary Ann McGahy, Resp’t, v. Catherine Duffy, Impl’d, App’lt.

No papers.

Ordered, That John McArdle, individually, and as administrator of the estate of Catherine Duffy, deceased, be and he is hereby substituted as a party defendant in the place of Catherine Duify, deceased, and this action is revived and continued in his name.
